    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Is the above solution (e.g. custom widget) still the recommended solution in v2 of Instantsearch to initialize third party plugins? \r\n\r\nFor most of the widgets we can now use the `templates` API in v2 to handle third party plugins. However, widgets like sortBySelector do not (yet?) have this feature.\r\n\r\nFor my use case I'm using Materialize which [uses a plugin](http://materializecss.com/forms.html#select-initialization) for styling `select` elements (among others).  ",
